"MAGICAL THEORY"

Magical theory allows you to understand and study ^Wmagic^n.  You do not have
to have magical ability to learn this skill (since it's a knowledge based
skill).  This skill is vital to anyone wishing to design spell formulas
or understand ^Wmagic^n.

^WSee Also: MAGIC, SORCERY, CONJURING, CREATE, LEARN, SPELLS^n

